<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Termux Website</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #282828;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 1em;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.5em;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #575757;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        main {
            display: flex;
            margin: 2em;
        }
        article {
            flex: 3;
            padding: 1em;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        aside {
            flex: 1;
            margin-left: 1em;
            padding: 1em;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #282828;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Termux Website</h1>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#setup">Setup</a>
        <a href="#usage">Usage</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <article>
            <h2>Welcome to Termux</h2>
            <p>This website provides information on using Termux, a powerful terminal emulator for Android.</p>
            <section id="setup">
                <h3>Setup</h3>
                <p>Learn how to install and configure Termux on your Android device.</p>
            </section>
            <section id="usage">
                <h3>Usage</h3>
                <p>Discover the various commands and tools available in Termux for development and automation.</p>
            </section>
        </article>
        <aside>
            <h2>Additional Resources</h2>
            <p>Check out these resources for more in-depth learning:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Termux Wiki</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Termux Packages</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Termux GitHub</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Termux Website. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
